<section class="portfolio-item">
	<h3 class="portfolio-item__title">riske photography</h3>
	<p class="portfolio-item__date">2019 - 2022</p>
	<figure class="portfolio-item__primary-img-wrapper">
		<%= image_tag('riske-primary.jpg',
				alt: 'images of a model from riskephotography.com') %>
	</figure>
	<span class="portfolio-item__text">Riske Photography is a professional boudoir photography company. I worked together with the client to build a unique and elegant website that stood out from other photographers in her niche and expressed a sophisticated ambiance. </span>
	<span class="portfolio-item__subtext">The client and I communicated remotely throughout the design process as well as in the years after for updates and general maintenance of the site.  I provided written explanations, screenshots, and video demos to teach her how to update and edit the content. I also wrote thorough documentation on coding processes and plugin usage for any future developers who might work on the site.</span>
	<div class="portfolio-item__environment">
		<h4>environment:</h4>
		<ul>
			<li>wordpress</li>
			<li>mailchimp</li>
			<li>zoom</li>
			<li>figma</li>
			<li>flowdesk</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<figure class="portfolio-item__secondary-img-wrapper">
		<%= image_tag('riske-secondary.jpg',
				alt: 'a screen capture of a headline from riskephotography.com') %>
	</figure>
</section>

<section class="portfolio-item">
	<h3 class="portfolio-item__title">engage nova scotia</h3>
	<p class="portfolio-item__date">december 2022</p>
	<figure class="portfolio-item__primary-img-wrapper">
		<%= image_tag('engage-primary.jpg',
				alt: 'a quote with design elements surrounding it') %>
	</figure>
	<span class="portfolio-item__text">Engage Nova Scotia is a non-profit working at the intersection of government, non-profit, business, and academic sectors. I worked for Engage as a data analytics intern to make recommendations on how they can share their NS Quality of Life Initiative data with various audiences across Canada. </span>
	<span class="portfolio-item__subtext">I organized the project management schedule for our research group using Asana and aimed to keep everyone on track with tasks and responsibilities. My research centered on identifying various data visualization techniques and how should be applied to different audiences. The project culminated in a series of interactive slides that I designed in Figma for Engage to use during employee training.</span>
	<div class="portfolio-item__environment">
		<h4>environment:</h4>
		<ul>
			<li>figma</li>
			<li>asana</li>
			<li>canva</li>
			<li>powerpoint</li>
			<li>zoom</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<figure class="portfolio-item__secondary-img-wrapper">
		<%= image_tag('engage-secondary.jpg',
				alt: 'a hand holding headphones linked to infographic bubbles') %>
	</figure>
</section>

