<section class="portfolio-item">
	<h3 class="portfolio-item__title">SSRIA</h3>
	<p class="portfolio-item__date">january 2022</p>
	<figure class="portfolio-item__primary-img-wrapper">
		<%= image_tag('ssria-primary.jpg',
				alt: 'a pie chart graph') %>
	</figure>
	<span class="portfolio-item__text">The Smart Sustainable Resilient Infrastructure Association (SSRIA) is a not-for-profit member-based association. As a statistical analysis intern for SSRIA, my responsibilities were to carry out a member satisfaction survey and perform market research. After the internship, I was reviewed as one of the top performing students in the program. </span>
	<span class="portfolio-item__subtext">I researched similar membership organizations to identify additional potential member benefits and presented the results in a report to the project manager. Then the manager and I designed a survey to analyze member satisfaction of association benefits and SSRIA’s overall missions and activities. After the survey responses were obtained, I performed statistical analysis on the results and provided a report on my findings.</span>
	<div class="portfolio-item__environment">
		<h4>environment:</h4>
		<ul>
			<li>statcrunch</li>
			<li>asana</li>
			<li>google meet</li>
			<li>google forms</li>
			<li>microsoft excel</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<figure class="portfolio-item__secondary-img-wrapper">
		<%= image_tag('ssria-secondary.jpg',
				alt: 'a snapshot of a statcrunch variable recoding') %>
	</figure>
</section>
